F1tX – Train. Track. Transform.

F1tX is your all-in-one fitness companion designed for Gen-Z and modern fitness enthusiasts.
With a vibrant design and motivating experience, F1tX helps you stay on track, form habits, and celebrate progress.

Key Features
	•	Personalized Workout Plans
Generate tailored workouts to match your fitness level and goals.
	•	Nutrition Guidance
Create balanced meal plans and log daily meals for better dietary awareness.
	•	Streaks & Progress Tracking
Stay consistent with daily and weekly streaks, track completed workouts, and measure growth.
	•	Awards & Achievements
Unlock colorful badges as you hit milestones and challenges.
	•	Motivational Messages
Get daily motivational quotes and reminders to keep you focused.
	•	Trendy UI & Experience
Bold visuals, vibrant gradient splash screen, and a gamified feel to make fitness fun.
